  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IECGDongleServiceWrapper
    interface for ECG Dongle service wrapper
    IECGDongleServiceWrapper.OnConnectedToServiceListener
    listener to be called when connected to the service
    IECGDongleServiceWrapper.OnDeviceConnectedListener
    listener to be called when a device is connected
    IECGDongleServiceWrapper.OnDeviceDisconnectedListener
    listener to be called when a device is disconnected
    IECGDongleServiceWrapper.OnDisconnectedFromServiceListener
    listener to be called when disconnected from ECG Dongle Framework service.
    IECGDongleServiceWrapper.OnFailedToStartScanListener
    listener to be called when we failed to start scan
    IECGDongleServiceWrapper.OnGotDevicesListener
    listener to be called when we get a list of connected devices (after connecting to service or after calling IECGDongleServiceWrapper.queryForDevices()
    IECGDongleServiceWrapper.OnNextDataReplyListener
    listener to be called when we've got next chunk of data from ECG Dongle Framework
    IECGDongleServiceWrapper.OnScanFiltersUpdatedListener
    listener to be called when scan filters changed
    IECGDongleServiceWrapper.OnScanStartedListener
    listener to be called when a scan is started
    IECGDongleServiceWrapper.OnScanStoppedListener
    listener to be called when scan stopped.
